  33:SynaptiX_FDK/lib/tinyusb/src/portable/st/stm32_fsdev/dcd_stm32_fsdev.c ****  * This driver has been tested with the following MCUs:
  34:SynaptiX_FDK/lib/tinyusb/src/portable/st/stm32_fsdev/dcd_stm32_fsdev.c ****  *  - F070, F072, L053, F042F6
  35:SynaptiX_FDK/lib/tinyusb/src/portable/st/stm32_fsdev/dcd_stm32_fsdev.c ****  *
  36:SynaptiX_FDK/lib/tinyusb/src/portable/st/stm32_fsdev/dcd_stm32_fsdev.c ****  * It also should work with minimal changes for any ST MCU with an "USB A"/"PCD"/"HCD" peripheral. 
