  40:SynaptiX_FDK/lib/tinyusb/src/portable/st/stm32_fsdev/dcd_stm32_fsdev.c ****  * F102, F103                      512 byte buffer; no internal D+ pull-up (maybe many more changes
  41:SynaptiX_FDK/lib/tinyusb/src/portable/st/stm32_fsdev/dcd_stm32_fsdev.c ****  * F302xB/C, F303xB/C, F373        512 byte buffer; no internal D+ pull-up
  42:SynaptiX_FDK/lib/tinyusb/src/portable/st/stm32_fsdev/dcd_stm32_fsdev.c ****  * F302x6/8, F302xD/E2, F303xD/E  1024 byte buffer; no internal D+ pull-up
